This paper deals with the problem of designing transmission policies for energy harvesting sensors to minimize the average age of information in the presence of erasures. This problem is related to information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), machine learning (cs.MA), and learning (cs.LG).
